item.title: [PI] Object ids?
item.dc:creator: @somebodyy somebodyy
item.description:
@somebodyy wrote:

This is easy,

go here; \src\server\world

Open up; ObjectManager.java

search for/add them;

	[code]c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(1032, 2605, 3156, 2, 10); //warning sign 
	c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(1032, 2603, 3156, 2, 10); //warning sign 
	c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(1032, 2602, 3155, 1, 10); //warning sign 
	c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(1032, 2602, 3153, 1, 10); //warning sign [/code]

But you might want to change the Coords though.
